&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in justify?&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&lt;BR&gt;2. SK's are supposed to be tied as the 2nd best tank but have the lowest damage avoidence of all melee classes. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in justify?&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&lt;BR&gt;3. SK spellbook needs to scale to evolving content better. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in justify?&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&lt;BR&gt;4. Revise the 68 points of SK AA's that weaken us by buying them. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
