&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in justify?&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&lt;BR&gt;6. Itemization revision. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
