&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0in justify?&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&lt;BR&gt;8. Our spell based aggro needs fixed and designed to scale. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; Verdana?&gt;&#xD;
